"pid":"3723b25b759f97e83a5833842d7389c2b7111d0c","tid":52238,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:16:01.000Z","msg":"整間lego博物館可能仲吸引"},{"pid":"7154dc44226a754dd1e476ee7ec351234c24746f","tid":52238,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T03:21:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>整間lego博物館可能仲吸引</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起lego land<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fe49c699fd76818c6860f619f94540ed465954f","tid":52238,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:04:17.000Z","msg":"其實都唔知有乜好展<br />\n故宮最正既文物老早就去晒台北故宮博物館<br />\n要睇建築就去北京<br />\n要睇文物就去台北<br />\n香港又搞真係不淪不類"},{"pid":"94c4af9de36f6790eb332c58162faec3f4e8c1ec","tid":52238,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8596fcb3e20c8674c691cbf450d62762935eb43","tid":52238,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起文藝藏館本身係好，好似巴黎倫敦咁間間博物館都係國寶。但依家執故宮二灘，送d豬頭骨黎放，有咩意思？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n根據北京故宮博物院網頁及內地報道，目前北京故宮藏品總量達180萬多套，以明清宮廷文物類藏品為主，而故宮每年舉辦約80個展覽，展出的文物只佔全部藏品不到1%。何慶基說，內地願意長期借出故宮藏品予香港，對香港帶來經濟好處，認為將成為香港其中一項最具吸引力的旅遊設施，但他說選址有問題，認為會破壞西九文化區的完整性（integrity）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161224/s00001/1482516764473\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161224%2Fs00001%2F1482516764473&d=iDv%2F7x6hUhJR8ARk1BOsyhpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=a03e7c26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161224%2Fs00001%2F1482516764473&h=65ef689c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20161224/s00001/1482516764473</a>"},{"pid":"fbd85ba13f72e554ed05533ea4511a281d8909ea","tid":52238,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:37:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2669a1a3fc3125673dc34eddf2dd6e3b2f5dbc1c","tid":52238,"uid":22378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:47:56.000Z","msg":"香港同北京故宮有咩關係？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246269fb4f6eb1e6f68289805546628dc1e07535","tid":52238,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T04:48:57.000Z","msg":"起响西九西到篤，西隧口擋住嗰個死位，真係搵鬼去"},{"pid":"9be21078e23accdfbaefe2c5c898db936e310bdb","tid":52238,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實都唔知有乜好展<br />\n故宮最正既文物老早就去晒台北故宮博物館<br />\n要睇建築就去北京<br />\n要睇文物就去台北<br />\n香港又搞真係不淪不類</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n兩個故官我都去過，支那果個到到都爛溶溶，d 展品同窗鋪哂塵無人理，盡顯支那大國風範<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5caec002d355cfbd91a916e036123a926473ed","tid":52238,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T05:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4948975e8373b6956579e800389d5e01adace36e","tid":52238,"uid":13594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T03:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd51e22b24677254c7abb9d0c213faa182c16a2a","tid":52238,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T04:36:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>整間lego博物館可能仲吸引</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n起lego land<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ad517d8